 2001-23232001-12-130,  ,  ,  IA&ND, 
PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the BIGSTONE CREE NATION BAND, of certain land in Alberta, as follows: (a) some 50 hectares as an addition to Wabasca Indian Reserve No. 166A, together with the mines and minerals existing within other parts of that reserve, and (b) another five hectares, mines and minerals included, as an addition to its Reserve No. 166.
